headline: Dow Jones Leader Amgen Leads These Biotech Stocks Heading Into Q4 Earnings Season
summary: Dow Jones biotech giant Amgen, along with fellow biotech stocks Gilead and Vertex, are due to report fourth-quarter earnings results soon.
